description: A curious energy calls from the Van Nuys Airport Observation Area, where the world's movements unfold beneath a watchful eye. Your task is to obtain 500 pennies from this unique vantage point. The reason is shrouded in the silent roar of the engines; merely gather what is needed, and do not question the whispers of fate.
